VI. CONCLUSION
In this article, we proposed a novel SEI method using KG-AFC based on adaptive signal feature embedded KG. The proposed KG-AFC innovatively combined the relevant characteristic of KG, uses KG to visually represent the extracted features, and stores them. In addition, with the feature weight layer based on the attention mechanism, the proposed KG-AFC algorithm was able to obtain the best combination strategy automatically. The simulation results proved that the KG-AFC achieved the balance between identification accuracy and computation overhead through the comparison of different compression ratios and different SEI methods. With the help of KG, we can analyze the RF signal more accurately through the visualization of the signal features.
